<h2 id="what-you-need">What You Need</h2>
<p>You donâ€™t need a lot of resources to do user testing. Support from your team is helpful, but at first you may need to conduct user tests by yourself in order to convince others of the benefits. Openness, humility, and curiosity are important qualities to embrace.</p>

<p>Specifically, itâ€™s good to have:</p>
<ul>
