  <li>A place to plan the user tests and take notes, like EtherPad/Riseup Pad Google Docs, or Notion</li>
  <li>Something to test, like your current software, a prototype, or a sketch</li>
  <li>(If possible) Another person to take notes during the test</li>
  <li>(If youâ€™re working remote) A video/audio conferencing tool, like Jitsi or Zoom</li>
